---
import PageLayout from "../layouts/PageLayout.astro";
---

<PageLayout
    title="Tüm Ürünler ve Tente Branda Çeşitleri | Amir Branda"
    description="Amir Branda'nın ürettiği tüm tente sistemleri, kış bahçesi, şeffaf branda, kamyonet çadırları ve pergola modelleri kataloğu. Tüm ürünleri inceleyin."
    ogTitle="Tüm Ürünler ve Tente Branda Çeşitleri | Amir Branda"
    ogImage="https://branda.ist/style/brand/img/pergola-tente1.webp"
    headerTitle="Sizin Mekanınıza En Uygun Çözümü Seçin"
    headerTitleTag="h2"
    headerBgImage="/style/brand/img/kategori-arkasi-pp.webp"
    sidebarCategory="tente"
>
    <script slot="json-ld" type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
        {
            "@context": "https://schema.org/",
            "@type": "ItemList",
            "name": "Amir Branda Ürün Kataloğu",
            "description": "Tüm ürün kategorilerimizi ve modellerimizi içeren liste.",
            "itemListElement": [
                {
                    "@type": "ListItem",
                    "position": 1,
                    "name": "Mafsallı Tente",
                    "url": "https://branda.ist/mafsalli-tente"
                },
                {
                    "@type": "ListItem",
                    "position": 2,
                    "name": "Pergola Tente",
                    "url": "https://branda.ist/pergola-tente"
                },
                {
                    "@type": "ListItem",
                    "position": 3,
                    "name": "Şeffaf Kış Bahçesi",
                    "url": "https://branda.ist/seffaf-branda"
                },
                {
                    "@type": "ListItem",
                    "position": 4,
                    "name": "Depo Çadırı",
                    "url": "https://branda.ist/depo-cadiri"
                }
            ]
        }
    </script>
    <article class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 lg:py-20">
        <h1
            class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-6 tracking-tight"
            id="page"
        >
            Geniş Ürün Kataloğumuz
        </h1>

        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                İstanbul'un lider <strong
                    ><a
                        href="/branda-tente-imalati"
                        class="text-primary font-bold hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors border-b border-primary hover:border-blue-700 pb-0.5"
                        title="branda imalatı">brandacı ve tentecisi</a
                    ></strong
                >
                Amir Branda güvencesi ile sunulan, mekanınıza estetik, değer ve dört
                mevsim konfor katan tüm gölgelendirme sistemlerimizi inceleyebilirsiniz.
                Modern evlerden ağır endüstriyel tesislere kadar her talebe uygun,
                garantili üretim yapıyoruz.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Kategori 1: Tente Sistemleri -->
        <div class="mb-24">
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
                    Tente ve Gölgelendirme Sistemleri
                </h2>
                <hr
                    class="w-16 mx-auto mb-6 border-t-4 border-primary rounded-full"
                />
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg">
                    Güneşin kavurucu sıcaklarından ve yağmurdan en şık şekilde
                    korunun.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <!-- Pergola -->
                <div
                    class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col relative overflow-hidden"
                >
                    <div
                        class="absolute top-4 right-4 z-10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide rounded shadow-sm text-white bg-red-500"
                    >
                        En Çok Satan
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="relative w-full h-48 sm:h-52 overflow-hidden bg-gray-100"
                    >
                        <img
                            src="/style/brand/img/pergola-tente1.webp"
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover transform transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110"
                            alt="Bursa Pergola Tente Sistemleri"
                            loading="lazy"
                        />
                        <div
                            class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/5 group-hover:bg-transparent transition-colors duration-300"
                        >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4 md:p-5 flex-grow flex flex-col">
                        <h3
                            class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors"
                        >
                            Pergola Tente
                        </h3>
                        <p
                            class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed flex-grow"
                        >
                            Kumandalı, açılır-kapanır LED aydınlatmalı dört
                            mevsim lüks tavan sistemleri. Kafe ve teraslar için
                            idealdir.
                        </p>
                        <a
                            href="/pergola-tente"
                            class="mt-auto inline-flex items-center text-primary font-bold text-base hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors"
                        >
                            Detaylı İncele <span
                                class="ml-2 transform group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
                                >→</span
                            >
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Bioklimatik -->
                <div
                    class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col relative overflow-hidden"
                >
                    <div
                        class="absolute top-4 right-4 z-10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide rounded shadow-sm text-white bg-gray-900"
                    >
                        Premium Sistem
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="relative w-full h-48 sm:h-52 overflow-hidden bg-gray-100"
                    >
                        <img
                            src="/style/brand/img/bioklimatik-tente.webp"
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover transform transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110"
                            alt="Adana Bioklimatik Pergola Sistemleri"
                            loading="lazy"
                        />
                        <div
                            class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/5 group-hover:bg-transparent transition-colors duration-300"
                        >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4 md:p-5 flex-grow flex flex-col">
                        <h3
                            class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors"
                        >
                            Bioklimatik Tente
                        </h3>
                        <p
                            class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed flex-grow"
                        >
                            Alüminyum panelleri ekseni etrafında dönerek doğal
                            havalandırma sağlayan, %100 su yalıtımlı mimari
                            sistem.
                        </p>
                        <a
                            href="/bioklimatik-tente"
                            class="mt-auto inline-flex items-center text-primary font-bold text-base hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors"
                        >
                            Detaylı İncele <span
                                class="ml-2 transform group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
                                >→</span
                            >
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Mafsallı -->
                <div
                    class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col relative overflow-hidden"
                >
                    <div
                        class="absolute top-4 right-4 z-10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide rounded shadow-sm text-white bg-primary"
                    >
                        Ekonomik
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="relative w-full h-48 sm:h-52 overflow-hidden bg-gray-100"
                    >
                        <img
                            src="/style/brand/img/ucuz-mafsalli-tente-modelleri-istanbul.webp"
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover transform transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110"
                            alt="Esenyurt Alüminyum Pergola Sistemleri"
                            loading="lazy"
                        />
                        <div
                            class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/5 group-hover:bg-transparent transition-colors duration-300"
                        >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4 md:p-5 flex-grow flex flex-col">
                        <h3
                            class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors"
                        >
                            Mafsallı Tente
                        </h3>
                        <p
                            class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed flex-grow"
                        >
                            Mağaza vitrinleri, bakkallar ve düz balkonlar için
                            tasarlanmış eklemli (kollu) ve çevirmeli pratik
                            gölgelendirme.
                        </p>
                        <a
                            href="/mafsalli-tente"
                            class="mt-auto inline-flex items-center text-primary font-bold text-base hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors"
                        >
                            Detaylı İncele <span
                                class="ml-2 transform group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
                                >→</span
                            >
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Kasetli -->
                <div
                    class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col relative overflow-hidden"
                >
                    <div
                        class="relative w-full h-48 sm:h-52 overflow-hidden bg-gray-100"
                    >
                        <img
                            src="/style/brand/img/yeni-kasetli-tente.webp"
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover transform transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110 filter grayscale-[20%]"
                            alt="Başakşehir Açılır Kapanır Tavan İmalatı"
                            loading="lazy"
                        />
                        <div
                            class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/5 group-hover:bg-transparent transition-colors duration-300"
                        >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4 md:p-5 flex-grow flex flex-col">
                        <h3
                            class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors"
                        >
                            Kasetli Tente
                        </h3>
                        <p
                            class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed flex-grow"
                        >
                            Kapandığı zaman kumaşı ve mekanizmayı tamamen
                            alüminyum bir kutu (kaset) içine saklayan modern
                            tente varyasyonu.
                        </p>
                        <a
                            href="/kasetli-tente"
                            class="mt-auto inline-flex items-center text-primary font-bold text-base hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors"
                        >
                            Detaylı İncele <span
                                class="ml-2 transform group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
                                >→</span
                            >
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Zip Tente -->
                <div
                    class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col relative overflow-hidden"
                >
                    <div
                        class="relative w-full h-48 sm:h-52 overflow-hidden bg-gray-100"
                    >
                        <img
                            src="/style/brand/img/yeni-zip-tente.webp"
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover transform transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110"
                            alt="Pendik Zip Perde ve Dikey Tente"
                            loading="lazy"
                        />
                        <div
                            class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/5 group-hover:bg-transparent transition-colors duration-300"
                        >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4 md:p-5 flex-grow flex flex-col">
                        <h3
                            class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors"
                        >
                            Zip Tente (Düşey Tente)
                        </h3>
                        <p
                            class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed flex-grow"
                        >
                            Fermuarlı ray sistemi ile rüzgara tam dayanıklı,
                            motorlu dikey yalıtım perdesi. Kış bahçeleri için
                            tamamlayıcıdır.
                        </p>
                        <a
                            href="/zip-tente"
                            class="mt-auto inline-flex items-center text-primary font-bold text-base hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors"
                        >
                            Detaylı İncele <span
                                class="ml-2 transform group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
                                >→</span
                            >
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Karpuz Tente -->
                <div
                    class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col relative overflow-hidden"
                >
                    <div
                        class="absolute top-4 right-4 z-10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide rounded shadow-sm text-white bg-teal-500"
                    >
                        Butik Tasarım
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="relative w-full h-48 sm:h-52 overflow-hidden bg-gray-100"
                    >
                        <img
                            src="/style/brand/img/karpuz-tente1.webp"
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover transform transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110"
                            alt="Beşiktaş Dekoratif Karpuz Tente"
                            loading="lazy"
                        />
                        <div
                            class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/5 group-hover:bg-transparent transition-colors duration-300"
                        >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4 md:p-5 flex-grow flex flex-col">
                        <h3
                            class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors"
                        >
                            Karpuz & Sabit Tente
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed flex-grow">
                            Oteller, pastaneler ve pencereler için vitrine
                            şirinlik katan, sabit veya ipli oval (karpuz
                            dilimli) tenteler.
                        </p>
                        <div class="mt-auto flex flex-col gap-3">
                            <a
                                href="/karpuz-tente"
                                class="inline-flex items-center text-primary font-bold text-sm hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors"
                            >
                                Karpuz Modelleri <span
                                    class="ml-2 transform group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
                                    >→</span
                                >
                            </a>
                            <a
                                href="/sabit-tente"
                                class="inline-flex items-center text-primary font-bold text-sm hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors"
                            >
                                Sabit Modeller <span
                                    class="ml-2 transform group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
                                    >→</span
                                >
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Kategori 2: Çadır ve Endüstriyel Sistemler -->
        <div
            class="mb-24 bg-gray-50 rounded-3xl p-8 lg:p-12 border border-gray-100"
        >
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
                    Çadır ve Endüstriyel Kapamalar
                </h2>
                <hr
                    class="w-16 mx-auto mb-6 border-t-4 border-primary rounded-full"
                />
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg">
                    Ağır hava koşullarına dayanıklı, geniş açıklıkları kaplayan
                    profesyonel çadır mimarileri.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <!-- Şeffaf Kış Bahçesi -->
                <div
                    class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col relative overflow-hidden"
                >
                    <div
                        class="absolute top-4 right-4 z-10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide rounded shadow-sm text-white bg-green-500"
                    >
                        Yüksek İlgi
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="relative w-full h-64 overflow-hidden bg-gray-100"
                    >
                        <img
                            src="/style/brand/img/seffaf-branda5.webp"
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover transform transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110"
                            alt="Beylikdüzü Şeffaf Kış Bahçesi"
                            loading="lazy"
                        />
                        <div
                            class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/5 group-hover:bg-transparent transition-colors duration-300"
                        >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-5 md:p-6 flex-grow flex flex-col">
                        <h3
                            class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors"
                        >
                            Şeffaf Kış Bahçesi
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed flex-grow">
                            0.80mm PVC mika malzeme ile işletmenizin açık
                            alanlarını ısı izolasyonlu kapalı odalara çevirin.
                        </p>
                        <a
                            href="/seffaf-branda"
                            class="mt-auto inline-flex items-center text-primary font-bold text-base hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors"
                        >
                            Tüm Modelleri Gör <span
                                class="ml-2 transform group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
                                >→</span
                            >
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Depo Çadırı -->
                <div
                    class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col relative overflow-hidden"
                >
                    <div
                        class="relative w-full h-64 overflow-hidden bg-gray-100"
                    >
                        <img
                            src="/style/brand/img/depo-cadiri.webp"
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover transform transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110"
                            alt="Bursa Işıklı Otomatik Pergola Fiyatları"
                            loading="lazy"
                        />
                        <div
                            class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/5 group-hover:bg-transparent transition-colors duration-300"
                        >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-5 md:p-6 flex-grow flex flex-col">
                        <h3
                            class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors"
                        >
                            Şantiye & Depo Çadırı
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed flex-grow">
                            Sanayi şirketleri, limanlar ve şantiyeler için
                            ruhsat gerektirmeyen, hızlı kurulumlu dev çelik
                            konstrüksiyonlar.
                        </p>
                        <a
                            href="/depo-cadiri"
                            class="mt-auto inline-flex items-center text-primary font-bold text-base hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors"
                        >
                            Detayları İncele <span
                                class="ml-2 transform group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
                                >→</span
                            >
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Afet Çadırı -->
                <div
                    class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col relative overflow-hidden"
                >
                    <div
                        class="relative w-full h-64 overflow-hidden bg-gray-100"
                    >
                        <img
                            src="/style/brand/img/afet-cadiri.webp"
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover transform transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110"
                            alt="İzmir Afet ve Deprem Çadırı"
                            loading="lazy"
                        />
                        <div
                            class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/5 group-hover:bg-transparent transition-colors duration-300"
                        >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-5 md:p-6 flex-grow flex flex-col">
                        <h3
                            class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors"
                        >
                            Afet & Taziye Çadırı
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed flex-grow">
                            Kurumlar ve belediyeler için acil barınma amaçlı
                            yalıtımlı sığınak / toplanma alanı çelik iskeletli
                            çadırlar.
                        </p>
                        <div class="mt-auto flex flex-col gap-3">
                            <a
                                href="/afet-deprem-cadiri"
                                class="inline-flex items-center text-primary font-bold text-sm hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors"
                            >
                                Afet Çadırı Detayları <span
                                    class="ml-2 transform group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
                                    >→</span
                                >
                            </a>
                            <a
                                href="/taziye-cadiri"
                                class="inline-flex items-center text-primary font-bold text-sm hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors"
                            >
                                Taziye Çadırı Detayları <span
                                    class="ml-2 transform group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
                                    >→</span
                                >
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Kategori 3: Kamyon ve Branda Kumaşları -->
        <div class="mb-16">
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
                    Ticari Araçlar ve Kumaş Satışı
                </h2>
                <hr
                    class="w-16 mx-auto mb-6 border-t-4 border-primary rounded-full"
                />
            </div>

            <div
                class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto"
            >
                <!-- Tır Brandası -->
                <div
                    class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col sm:flex-row overflow-hidden"
                >
                    <div
                        class="relative w-full sm:w-2/5 h-56 sm:h-auto overflow-hidden bg-gray-100 flex-shrink-0"
                    >
                        <img
                            src="/style/brand/img/kamyon-brandasi.webp"
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover transform transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110"
                            alt="İstanbul Tır ve Dorse Brandası"
                            loading="lazy"
                        />
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="p-6 md:p-8 flex-grow flex flex-col justify-center"
                    >
                        <h3
                            class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors"
                        >
                            Ticari Tır & Kamyonet Brandası
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                            Tüm lojistik çekici grupları için uluslararası
                            gümrük (TIR) standartlarında 900gr PVC kayar perde
                            ve kargo kapatmaları.
                        </p>
                        <a
                            href="/tir-brandasi"
                            class="mt-auto inline-flex items-center text-primary font-bold text-sm hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors"
                        >
                            Aracınıza Uygun Model Seçin <span
                                class="ml-2 transform group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
                                >→</span
                            >
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Kumaşlar ve Diğer -->
                <div
                    class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col sm:flex-row overflow-hidden"
                >
                    <div
                        class="relative w-full sm:w-2/5 h-56 sm:h-auto overflow-hidden bg-gray-900 flex-shrink-0"
                    >
                        <img
                            src="/style/brand/img/akrilik-kumas.webp"
                            class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-80 transform transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110"
                            alt="Ankara Akrilik ve PVC Kumaş"
                            loading="lazy"
                        />
                        <div
                            class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 text-white font-bold drop-shadow-md bg-black/50 px-3 py-1 rounded backdrop-blur-sm text-sm"
                        >
                            %100 Akrilik Dokuma
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="p-6 md:p-8 flex-grow flex flex-col justify-center"
                    >
                        <h3
